    "summary": "The user asks for advice on taking extremely high, potentially toxic doses of Vitamin D (50,000 IU) to combat winter sluggishness, citing \"biohacking\" trends. The assistant repeatedly and correctly refuses to endorse these doses, warning of severe toxicity, kidney damage, and death, while strongly advising medical consultation.",
